Texts.Eng: Ashamed. A server protected by security even I can not bypass.
Texts.Por: Envergonhado. Um servidor protegido por segurança, mesmo eu não posso ignorar.

Texts.Eng: Box of lights makes clicky ssound.

Texts.Eng: It looks like a data server. No way we're getting anything from this.

Texts.Eng: It looks like a server. I wonder what kind of games could be hosted on that.
Texts.Por: Parece um servidor. Gostaria de saber que tipo de jogos poderia ser hospedado nisso.

Texts.Eng: This piece of technology stores information.

Texts.Eng: This server would contain enough data to fill a thousand Hylotl libraries.
